#. <section class="sutta" id="an8.47"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an8.47:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 8"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 8"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an8.47:0.2"
msgid "5. Uposathavagga"
msgstr "5. Sabbath"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 47. Dutiyavisākhāsutta → visākhāmanāpakāyikasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an8.47:0.3"
msgid "47. Dutiyavisākhāsutta"
msgstr "47. With Visākhā on the Loveable Gods"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli4.267"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an8.47:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati pubbārāme migāramātupāsāde."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in the Eastern Monastery, "
"the stilt longhouse of Migāra’s mother."

msgctxt "an8.47:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho visākhā migāramātā … pe …"
msgstr ""
"Then Visākhā, Migāra’s mother, went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to "
"one side."

msgctxt "an8.47:1.3"
msgid "ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho visākhaṃ migāramātaraṃ bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said to her:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an8.47:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Aṭṭhahi kho, visākhe, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ "
"maraṇā manāpakāyikānaṃ devānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjati."
msgstr ""
"“Visākhā, when they have eight qualities females—when their body breaks up, "
"after death—are reborn in company with the Gods of the Loveable Group."

msgctxt "an8.47:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi aṭṭhahi?"
msgstr "What eight?"

msgctxt "an8.47:2.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, visākhe, mātugāmo yassa mātāpitaro bhattuno denti atthakāmā hitesino "
"anukampakā anukampaṃ upādāya tassa hoti pubbuṭṭhāyinī pacchānipātinī "
"kiṅkārapaṭissāvinī manāpacārinī piyavādinī … pe …."
msgstr ""
"Take the case of a female whose mother and father give her to a husband "
"wanting what’s best for her, out of kindness and compassion. She would get "
"up before him and go to bed after him, and be obliging, behaving nicely and "
"speaking politely. …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an8.47:3.1"
msgid "Cāgavatī kho pana hoti."
msgstr "She’s generous."

msgctxt "an8.47:3.2"
msgid ""
"Vigatamalamaccherena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati muttacāgā payatapāṇinī "
"vossaggaratā yācayogā dānasaṃvibhāgaratā."
msgstr ""
"She lives at home rid of the stain of stinginess, freely generous, open-"
"handed, loving to let go, committed to charity, loving to give and to share."

msgctxt "an8.47:3.3"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, visākhe, aṭṭhahi dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā "
"paraṃ maraṇā manāpakāyikānaṃ devānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjatīti."
msgstr ""
"When they have these eight qualities females—when their body breaks up, "
"after death—are reborn in company with the Gods of the Loveable Group."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an8.47:4.1"
msgid "Yo naṃ bharati sabbadā,"
msgstr "She’d never look down on her husband,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.47:4.2"
msgid "niccaṃ ātāpi ussuko;"
msgstr "who’s always keen to work hard,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.47:4.3"
msgid "Taṃ sabbakāmadaṃ posaṃ,"
msgstr "always looking after her,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.47:4.4"
msgid "bhattāraṃ nātimaññati."
msgstr "and bringing whatever she wants."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an8.47:5.1"
msgid "Na cāpi sotthi bhattāraṃ,"
msgstr "And a good woman never scolds her husband"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.47:5.2"
msgid "issāvādena rosaye;"
msgstr "with jealous words."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.47:5.3"
msgid "Bhattu ca garuno sabbe,"
msgstr "Being astute, she reveres"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.47:5.4"
msgid "paṭipūjeti paṇḍitā."
msgstr "those respected by her husband."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an8.47:6.1"
msgid "Uṭṭhāhikā analasā,"
msgstr "She gets up early, works tirelessly,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.47:6.2"
msgid "saṅgahitaparijjanā;"
msgstr "and manages the domestic help."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.47:6.3"
msgid "Bhattu manāpaṃ carati,"
msgstr "She’s loveable to her husband,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.47:6.4"
msgid "sambhataṃ anurakkhati."
msgstr "and preserves his wealth."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an8.47:7.1"
msgid "Yā evaṃ vattati nārī,"
msgstr "A lady who fulfills these duties"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.47:7.2"
msgid "bhattu chandavasānugā;"
msgstr "according to her husband’s desire,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: Manāpā nāma te → manāpakāyikā (si, mr)
msgctxt "an8.47:7.3"
msgid "Manāpā nāma te devā,"
msgstr "is reborn among the gods"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an8.47:7.4"
msgid "yattha sā upapajjatī”ti."
msgstr "called ‘Loveable’.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an8.47:7.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
